Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:40.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost a week since I started\Naimlessly pedaling my bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:46.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I withdrew some money and bought a\Nlot of things from the 100 yen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:51.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The compass, the map of Japan, and\Nthe wristwatch are especially useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With these, I can finally travel with a plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:04.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What surprised me the most on my journey was how quickly you\Nbecome hungry when you've been pedaling the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I quickly lose strength if I don't eat at least five times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:15.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned very well that the food you\Neat acts as gasoline for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:21.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What surprised me was that there aren't\Nmany places to camp out in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:30.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of open space, but people can't sleep\Nrestfully unless they're by a tree or a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I learned for the first time on my travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather stressful to get water where\Nthere aren't any public facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:44.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:55.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, people gradiously share some with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, events like this aren't rare either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to ask many different people, but I get nervous every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And as I saw these various homes I began to think this way:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:24.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Homes and the people that live in them resemble each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got so much baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:37.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Bag: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Supermarket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only water, but even food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:54.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to liken me to a house, I wonder what I'd look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I look like that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've outdone yourself again, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a toughie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go with the milk white?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ash gray is hard to pass up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san, it's a text message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's from Nomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:37.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H517254&\bord0\fs28\b0\fscx70\fnArial\shad0\move(401,258,401,306)\c&H314530&\frz19.564\frx348\fry6}Nomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:37.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H517254&\bord0\fs22\b0\fscx70\fnArial\shad0\move(433,458,433,504)\frz19.564\c&H445845&\frx354\fry358}I still haven't seen the dunes.\NLuigi sucks.\NHe just abandoned all his work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, please send him a message to encourage him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I don't have a cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you don't have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll send one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:55.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sure it's tough, but please watch your health\Nand do your best with your job in Tottori."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's so dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something you want to say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like about how he went to Tottori without telling you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:11.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true. If he's going to be gone in Tottori for half a year,\Nhe should've just told me when I saw him the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:15.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Ah! Miwako-san, you don't need to type all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\3c&HEEEFF1&\shad0\bord1\be1\fs46\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp1\move(330,109,241,109)\c&H72A6DF&}Whoa... Miwako-san, you're too fast.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hI can't keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't need to type all that," got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the message say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Nomiya, your ears are red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.95,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.54,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing feeling pressured\Nover a kid? You're so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.13,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like there might be a chance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.04,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.34,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,From Miwako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:01.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs76\fsp1\bord0\shad0\i1\b0\frz42.92\1a&32&\be1\c&H9FB198&\frx356\fry358\pos(279,254)}INBOX
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:01.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H15180F&\bord0\shad0\i1\b0\fscx80\fsp5\fs110\be1\frx0\fry0\frz43.701\pos(398,285)}MIWAKO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now... she's a terrifying person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you didn't submit a piece to the Marine\NLight Exhibit or the Four Seasons Exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've become the youngest person to win an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you don't do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:30.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been invited to study at an art school in Italy, but I hear\Nthat you're going back to the countryside after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:33.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Art isn't so easy that you can improve\Nyour skills out in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:39.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the ability to make anything possible,\Nif you just gave it a try. So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouda-sensei, Hagu will keep drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's returning to the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please don't think of her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:15.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouda-sensei, you see, has been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:21.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to become a painter, studied alone in Paris\Nfor many years, and worked so hard she became ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:28.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think she's agitated by your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:34.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, I think Kouda-sensei's opinion is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that her opinion is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:45.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is that no matter what path you\Nchoose, you don't make an excuse out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My savings are almost half gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move forward without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When my money is half gone is when I have to turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did I run out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where am I headed to?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"What will I find if I keep going like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe I should head back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These thoughts plagued my mind as I went along my travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I still can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:12.33,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}makka na tsuki ga yobu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:12.33,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}The crimson moon calls me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:22.04,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}boku ga umareta tokoro sa doko darou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:22.04,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}I was born there... but where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:27.80,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kiiroi tsuki ga yobu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:27.80,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}The yellow moon calls you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:35.18,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kimi ga umareta tokoro sa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:35.18,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}It's where you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:41.85,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}shimetta kibako no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:41.85,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}It looks like we were able to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:47.69,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}meguriaeta mitai da ne
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:47.69,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Inside that damp wooden box
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:55.33,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}kyou no hi yukai ni sugiteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:55.33,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Today is fun and passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:10:10.43,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}mou sayonara da yo kimi no koto wa wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:10:10.43,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}It's time to say goodbye now, I won't forget about you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Passing through the tunnel, I came to a really beautiful spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first tourist spot that I've visited on my trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:36.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a place you'd normally\Ncome to on a bullet train from Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it here on a bicycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:43.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little... just a little... proud of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Buigan-ji, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've been to a Buddhist temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs50\pos(422,69)\frx15\fry2\c&H3F3F33&\3c&H3E3D32&}Admission Ticket Vending
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs35\frx15\fry0\pos(312,141)\3c&H4C4C43&\c&H49493F&}ADULTS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs23\frx5\fry0\3c&H64655A&\pos(299,205)\c&H5C5B50&}(incl. College, School, Sr. High)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs35\pos(552,202)\frx15\fry8\c&H74786D&\3c&H74786D&}700 YEN
