Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\shad0\bord0\b1\pos(423,373)\frx7\c&H939890&\fscx80\fsp1\frz0.466}For those who are here by themselves, please use the ticket vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Admission is 700 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:58.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is frustrating... it's right in front\Nof me, but I can only see the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the gate by itself is plenty impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For an age without fret-saws or slicers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:15.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, my mind was only on pedaling,\Nand I hadn't been looking at the scenery, like temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should start looking at temples from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've come this far, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:27.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:55.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do now? My bicycle's totaled...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, white fellow, any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach can rumble all it wants but you're not getting any!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I... wasn't thinking of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san, eat it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made that bento with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt, your bento has too much rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are too little sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:28.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You fill the damn thing with just pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some real sides, like something fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the green cayenne pepper is too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hit the pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:45.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're restoration workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it might be more accurate to call us temple carpenters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We go around the country fixing Buddhist and Shinto temples,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,and once one work is complete, we move on to the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always moving around, just like nomads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our chief is at a different temple right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm the director here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's start our afternoon work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:25.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty worn... it might be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you ride this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:52.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you came all the way to Sendai\Nwith this old one-gear bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, from Tokyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an absentee in the Sandai-ji group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyoshi is going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasu and Taka need to gather up their belongings\Nand move to Kyoto tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If two of our members leave, what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:19.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, that's why I was opposed to letting Kiyoshi in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The youngsters these days can't be trusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you 18-year-old!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're precisely one of those "youngsters these days"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:29.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, they don't have much time until the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave things over here to you, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please handle operations and checks, Kamekichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may I please work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What I learned in school might not be of any use here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'll do anything, even throw away scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make money to fix my bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:57.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:15:59.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the construction coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The work's cheap and tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Takemoto-kun is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope that he's been able to find at least a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Takemoto-kun isn't lonely all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:52.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness comes over you like a wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then disappears before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it goes, on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:03.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Takemoto, I'm reminiscing about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada, I'm lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the eleventh day for Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which floor for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my goodness! The two of you came together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been heavy, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've sent a car over if you just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.79,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.88,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is coffee okay for both of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! It's not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.61,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the person Mayama is in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The unexpected duet of dreams by the two stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me, Nomiya, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.79,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... I need to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's Mayama today...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out at a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm a year younger than Mayama-kun,\Nbut we were in the same class...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:40.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been working for this place,\Nhalf thanks to his introduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.61,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that Mayama isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.11,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.91,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That I didn't have to see the two of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.78,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really make beautiful dishes, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hand-twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My heel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\3c&HEEEFF1&\shad0\bord1\fs46\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp3\c&H9BCCF2&\pos(160,155)}I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:12.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been thinking lately that my heels were sounding creaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm actually pretty good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:24.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I swapped out the filling inside the insole and\Nmade emergency repairs with super glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it tomorrow to the store that I bought this at for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:28.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a delicate and beautiful shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's her favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's been wearing it gently for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are signs that it's been fixed a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Mayama fixed it for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you met Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:56.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed to me like she wasn't taking proper care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:01.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's so emaciated and needs to use a cane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She wears such delicate-looking high heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Rika's treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her late husband bought them for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More so than herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so full of wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for driving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamabi is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:55.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:01.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that it might be dangerous for you to\Nbe wearing shoes with such high heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She smiled a little as she said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:16.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a flower soaked in the rain.
